            </div>
            <div>
                <h2><a name="TestHeader"></a>Test - Header</h2>
                <MadCap:snippetBlock src="application-test-header.flsnp" />
            </div>
            <div class="noteOkta">
                <p class="noteContent">When the <span class="uicontrol">Debug</span> mode is activated on production applications, it can impact the performance. When complete, always reset the <span class="uicontrol">Protected Web Resource</span> field and deactivate the <span class="uicontrol">Debug</span> mode toggle. </p>
            </div>
